            <div class="field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field--item"><p></p><figure role="group" aria-label="We welcome all visitors to visit CEE and UC Berkeley, including prospective students and their families. (Credit: Adam Lau)" class="align-left">
